	---1---
		Title: Showing a question.
		Description:There is a question and you have four answer from which you can choose the right one.After you choose your 			answer the application will show you if you are right or wrong.

	---2---
		Title:Going to the next question
		Description: If your answer is true you will go on to the next question.There will be a counter showing how many questions  			you have answered right.

